16/08/2009
BUCHAREST, Romania -- Prime Minister Emil Boc announced on Friday (August 14th) that three ministries -- interior, justice and education -- will receive additional funds as the budget is revised in the weeks ahead. 
Boc added that everyone employed in the education and interior ministries will receive their salaries, and said that additional funds will be earmarked for the unemployed. 
(Mediafax, Hotnews.ro - 14/08/09)
